room_title: Escape room "Swan Song" by 601 Escape Rooms in Jackson (MS)
room_description:
Dean Waylon is the frontman of the band 'Us, Them or Dean'. Tonight they will be performing the kick-off show of their concert run at the Colosseum Resort and Casino in Las Vegas. Dean has recently announced this will be his final tour resulting in a sold-out show. As the music reporter for a local paper, you’ve got your backstage pass, and you’re eager to interview Dean before the show.
Dean is late for the show and the crowd starts to get restless. You sneak into Dean’s dressing room to retrace the career of Dean Waylon and determine why he is late for the show. It’s all up to you to solve the clues and figure out what is going on without getting caught by security!
